\c 17
\s Isivumelwano sikaNkulunkulu loDavida
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi uDavida esehlezi endlini yakhe, uDavida wathi kuNathani umprofethi: Khangela, mina ngihlala endlini yemisedari, kodwa umtshokotsho wesivumelwano seN\nd kosi\nd* ungaphansi kwamakhetheni\x + 2 Sam. 7.1-29.\x*.
\v 2 UNathani wasesithi kuDavida: Yenza konke okusenhliziyweni yakho, ngoba uNkulunkulu ulawe.
\p
\v 3 Kodwa kwathi ngabona lobobusuku ilizwi likaNkulunkulu lafika kuNathani, lisithi:
\v 4 Hamba utshele uDavida inceku yami: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Wena kawuyikungakhela indlu yokuhlala.
\v 5 Ngoba kangihlalanga endlini kusukela osukwini engenyusa ngalo uIsrayeli kuze kube lamuhla, kodwa ngasuka ethenteni ngaya ethenteni njalo ngasuka ethabhanekeleni \add ngaya kwelinye\add*.
\v 6 Loba ngaphi engihambe khona loIsrayeli wonke ngake ngakhuluma ilizwi yini komunye wabahluleli bakoIsrayeli, engabalaya ukwelusa abantu bami ngisithi: Yini lingangakhelanga indlu yemisedari\x + 2 Sam. 7.7.\x*?
\v 7 Ngakho-ke uzakutsho njalo encekwini yami uDavida \add uthi\add*: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla: Mina ngakuthatha esibayeni sezimvu ekulandeleni izimvu ukuze ube ngumbusi phezu kwabantu bami uIsrayeli.
\v 8 Njalo ngaba lawe loba ngaphi oya khona, ngaquma zonke izitha zakho zasuka phambi kwakho, ngakwenzela ibizo njengebizo labakhulu abasemhlabeni.
\v 9 Njalo ngizabamisela indawo abantu bami uIsrayeli, ngibagxumeke ukuze bahlale endaweni yabo, bangabe besanyikinywa; labantwana bobubi kabasayikubamotsha njengakuqala\x + Hlab. 49.14.\x*,
\v 10 njalo kusukela kulezonsuku engalaya abahluleli ukuthi babe phezu kwabantu bami uIsrayeli; ngazehlisela phansi zonke izitha zakho; njalo ngiyakutshela ukuthi iNKOSI izakwakhela indlu.
\p
\v 11 Kuzakuthi-ke lapho insuku zakho sezigcwalisekile ukuthi uhambe laboyihlo, ngizavusa inzalo yakho emva kwakho, ezavela emadodaneni akho, ngiqinise umbuso wayo.
\v 12 Yena uzangakhela indlu, ngizaqinisa isihlalo sakhe sobukhosi kuze kube nininini.
\v 13 Mina ngizakuba nguyise, yena abe yindodana yami; njalo kangiyikususa uthandolomusa wami kuye\x + Heb. 1.5.\x* njengalokho ngalususa kulowo owayengaphambi kwakho\x + 2 Sam. 7.15.\x*.
\v 14 Kodwa ngizamqinisa endlini yami lembusweni wami kuze kube nininini, lesihlalo sakhe sobukhosi sizaqiniswa kuze kube nininini.
\v 15 Njengawo wonke lamazwi lanjengawo wonke lumbono, ngokunjalo uNathani wakhuluma kuDavida.
\p
\v 16 Inkosi uDavida yasingena yahlala phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, yathi: Mina ngingubani, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu, lendlu yami iyini, ukuthi ungilethe kuze kube lapha?
\v 17 Lokhu bekukuncinyane emehlweni akho, Nkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 7.19.\x*; usukhulumile ngendlu yenceku yakho kusesekhatshana\x + 2 Sam. 7.19.\x*, wangibona\x + Dute. 33.9.\x* ngokwesikhundla somuntu ophakemeyo, N\nd kosi\nd* Nkulunkulu\x + 2 Sam. 7.19.\x*.
\v 18 UDavida angenzani okunye kuwe ngodumo lwenceku yakho? Ngoba wena uyayazi inceku yakho.
\v 19 N\nd kosi\nd*, ngenxa yenceku yakho langokwenhliziyo yakho wenzile zonke lezizinto ezinkulu ukwazisa zonke lezizinto ezinkulu\x + 2 Sam. 7.21.\x*.
\v 20 N\nd kosi\nd*, kakho onjengawe, njalo kakho uNkulunkulu ngaphandle kwakho, njengakho konke esikuzwileyo ngendlebe zethu.
\v 21 Njalo ngubani onjengabantu bakho uIsrayeli, isizwe esisodwa emhlabeni, uNkulunkulu owayazihlengela sona sibe ngabantu, ukuzenzela ibizo \add nge\add*zenzo ezinkulu lezesabekayo, ngokuxotsha elifeni izizwe ukuzisusa phambi kwabantu bakho owabahlenga eGibhithe?
\v 22 Ngoba wenza abantu bakho uIsrayeli ukuthi babe ngabantu bakho kuze kube nininini; lawe N\nd kosi\nd* waba nguNkulunkulu wabo.
\v 23 Khathesi-ke, N\nd kosi\nd*, ilizwi owalikhuluma ngenceku yakho langendlu yayo kaliqiniswe kuze kube nininini, wenze njengokukhuluma kwakho.
\v 24 Yebo kaliqiniswe, lebizo lakho kalibe likhulu kuze kube nininini, kuthiwa: IN\nd kosi\nd* yamabandla inguNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli, nguNkulunkulu koIsrayeli; lendlu kaDavida inceku yakho kayimiswe phambi kwakho.
\v 25 Ngoba wena, Nkulunkulu wami, wembule endlebeni yenceku yakho ukuthi uzayakhela indlu; ngenxa yalokho inceku yakho ithole \add enhliziyweni \add*ukukhuleka phambi kwakho\x + 2 Sam. 7.27.\x*.
\v 26 Khathesi-ke, N\nd kosi\nd*, wena unguye uNkulunkulu, ukhulume lokhu okuhle ngenceku yakho.
\v 27 Khathesi-ke, kukuthokozisile ukubusisa indlu yenceku yakho ukuze ibe phambi kwakho kuze kube nininini; ngoba, wena N\nd kosi\nd*, uyabusisa, njalo izabusiswa kuze kube nini lanini.
